<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Chen's blog (Posts about torrent)</title><link>http://blog.binchen.org/</link><description></description><atom:link href="http://blog.binchen.org/categories/torrent.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:11:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Use screen/rtorrent/cronie to manage torrent client</title><link>http://blog.binchen.org/posts/use-screenrtorrentcronie-to-manage-torrent-client/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;p&gt;
`man rtorrent` for the keybindings:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="org-ul"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;`Enter` to input magnet from piratebay manually&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;`C-s` to start download&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;`C-d` to delete&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
For &lt;a href="http://www.archlinux.org"&gt;ArchLinux&lt;/a&gt; only:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id="outline-container-org52201c6" class="outline-2"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="org52201c6"&gt;Prepare directory&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org52201c6"&gt;
&lt;div class="org-src-container"&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="lang-sh"&gt;mkdir -p ~/bt/{session,finished,torrent}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id="outline-container-org7daf396" class="outline-2"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="org7daf396"&gt;Install&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org7daf396"&gt;
&lt;div class="org-src-container"&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="lang-sh"&gt;sudo pacman -S cronie
sudo systemctl enable cronie
sudo systemctl start cronie
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id="outline-container-org38720cb" class="outline-2"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="org38720cb"&gt;Add cron task to start and stop rtorrent service&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org38720cb"&gt;
&lt;div class="org-src-container"&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="lang-sh"&gt;crontab -e #add cron task as current user
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
The default editor will be open, input below content:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="org-src-container"&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="lang-ini"&gt;#start rtorrent sesssion at 1am
0 1 * * * /usr/bin/screen -fa -d -m -S torrent /usr/bin/rtorrent
# kill it at  9am
0 10 * * * /usr/bin/screen -S torrent -X quit
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Done!
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
